precis:
Enactment of the CANADIAN AVIATION SECURITY REGULATIONS which combine the
requirements of the Air Carrier Security Regulations and the Aerodrome
Security Regulations in one set of Regulations and impose new or stricter
security requirements on air carriers and airport authorities.
